item.itunes:title: Paleolithic Deep State
item.description:
Today we travel to Antarctica to investigate two mysterious deaths, then head back in time to find out what is going on with the Paleolithic Deep State.

Patreon
https://www.patreon.com/user?u=18482113

MERCH STORE!!!
https://tinyurl.com/y8zam4o2

Recently, two men died in Antarctica. No cause of death, or names, have been revealed for the unlucky duo. What happened on the unexplored continent?

Then we revisit the Conspiracy Iceberg to investigate the mysterious Paleolithic Deep State.
